messages.content: What is the purpose of ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH?
ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH is a custom node or plugin that extends the functionality of ComfyUI, a GUI that uses stable diffusion models to generate images and videos.
Where did the code for Face Detection in ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH come from?
The code for Face Detection in ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH was taken from the face_alignment repository on GitHub.
Who is the author of the face_alignment repository?
The face_alignment repository is authored by 1adrianb on GitHub.
How has the face_alignment code been modified in ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH?
In ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH, the face_alignment code has been modified to take batches of faces at a time.
No, ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH is not a standalone application. It is a custom node or plugin that extends the functionality of the ComfyUI application.
What is the main functionality of the face_alignment code used in ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH?
The main functionality of the face_alignment code used in ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH is to perform face detection.
Does ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH process single or multiple faces at a time?
ComfyUI-MuseTalk_FSH processes multiple faces at a time, as the face_alignment code has been modified to take batches of faces.
